content:
Welcome to Scratchpad!

This is a simple web application written in VueJS and built with Webpack. It uses `LocalStorage` to store data, and automatically saves your notes when you finish typing.

The note you're reading is supposed to give you a glimpse at what Scratchpad can do.

- Add, modify and delete individual notes;
- The first line will always be your note's title;
- Use hashtags to tag your notes, throughout the content (it's best to keep them in the last line);
- Export all notes to a JSON file.

There are probably bugs and other bits that aren't necessarily tested, but given the timeframe, it was an interesting exercise, so thanks!

-Matthew

#tutorial #deleteme
